{"tid":1569250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【警狗收皮】「國難五金」被警方搜查近兩小時無帶走任何貨品","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:00:25.000Z","uid":175314,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"24684a50c3948716e4765eb920b3287519b2623d","tid":1569250,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ix4z0T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ix4z0T.jpg&h=e094d9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/9RDY2x?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F9RDY2x%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=cde9cbab\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/9RDY2x?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n原本在西營盤開舖營業，售賣防毒面具等裝備的「國難五金」，宣布在深水埗開設「旗艦店」，惟今日開張不久即被警方「掃場」，<span style=\"color: red;\">多名警員帶同法庭搜查令搜查店舖，搜索近兩小時後離開，無帶走任何貨品。</span><br />\n<br />\n「國難五金」開張慶典在下午 3 時舉行，惟警方在大約 5 時帶同法庭搜查令來到長沙灣道的店舖現場，他們在店內紀錄各箱防毒面具等物資的編號、數量等，而舖頭東主和其代表律師亦在店內觀察搜查過程。<br />\n<br />\n除了在店內搜查的警員外，警方亦派出最少 30 名機動部隊警員在舖頭門外，以至兩邊行人路把守，不准任何人走近。期間一名店員在舖頭對面行人路開直播，呼籲顧客前來聲援。及後，50 名市民來到聲援，並在現場觀察搜查情況，期間叫口號和唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n大概在 6 時 45 分左右，在店內搜查的警員結束搜查工作，離開舖頭，店外的機動部隊警員亦收起封鎖線收隊，步行到兩個街口外的警車，離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n國難五金東主說，警方只紀錄店內貨品的詳細資訊，沒帶走任何貨品，又說警方搜遍全店，紀錄好全部貨品，「咁就證明我真係做正當生意」。之後，老闆宣布開張慶典繼續舉行，請在場街坊和顧客食燒豬，30 名顧客亦排隊入舖光顧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">狗又攪事</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d854a39c663a54886ba03a9f4908f08076e0f5c","tid":1569250,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a34877a1ca836aa27edadca022a745a96aa4716","tid":1569250,"uid":255493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"擾民"},{"pid":"26e9c5daf1cda7fd0960b9c9ef7837c5a0d86566","tid":1569250,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d854a39c663a54886ba03a9f4908f08076e0f5c","tid":1569250,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"仲慘黨就真<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb0bf063ee0af635d17a904a32d375588b3e644","tid":1569250,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a34877a1ca836aa27edadca022a745a96aa4716","tid":1569250,"uid":255493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"擾民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"放狗周圍咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fe1409dc47c5114390321024bc7644f2b0b49","tid":1569250,"uid":271234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"5e1a47e5d429e2925a5447b9b1db2c32caf1b9a7","tid":1569250,"uid":281342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src